
The release 1.1 (Loquat) of Flora-2 fixes a number of bugs and adds new
features. This release includes self-contained Windows, Mac, and Linux
installers.

The installer flora2.run is for Linux/Mac/Cygwin/Other Unixes users.
The installer Flora-2.exe is for Windows users.

Details can be found in the release notes at
http://flora.sourceforge.net/release_notes.html
and the installation instructions are at
http://flora.sourceforge.net/installation.html
